# FHI Metallic Shimmers Color Specifier and Guide Set

## Bundle two formats for double the versatility

Sku#: FHIP530B

$ 466.00

Add To Cart

Expand your Pantone Fashion, Home + Interiors (FHI) color palette with 200 new luxurious metallic finishes when working with fashion accessories, footwear, electronics, housewares, and interiors. The set includes the Metallic Shimmers Color Guide as a portable reference tool with one full-bleed color per page, and the Metallic Shimmers Color Specifier with removable paper chips for palette development, mood boards, product sketches, or attach to design files for communicating color.

- A trend-driven selection of metallic colors to broaden and compliment Pantone’s (Fashion, Home + Interiors) FHI System
- Metallics add premium impact to designs for products and interiors
- Fan-format Color Guide and desktop binder-format Color Specifier bundled together

